{"tid":339428,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Corsair 被 EagleTree Capital 以 5.25 億美元收購","createTime":"2017-07-29T05:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T12:14:49.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b8c748a1da11395ea53a954fde48808c716f88","tid":339428,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/TangBao/170727-corsair-logo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FTangBao%2F170727-corsair-logo.jpg&h=5c0665e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/32759/corsair-confirms-majority-share-525-million-acquisition-deal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F32759%2Fcorsair-confirms-majority-share-525-million-acquisition-deal&d=Khx3AQKzWih%2FwQaBBRTJcQEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=160468a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/32759/corsair-confirms-majority-share-525-million-acquisition-deal</a></div><br />\n<br />\n大家很熟悉的美國電競周邊商 Corsair（海盜船），現傳出被收購訊息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。看準電競市場潛力的投資團隊 EagleTree Capital，用 5.25 億美元收購 Corsair 多數股票，成為最大股東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n <br />\n根據官方新聞稿顯示，Corsair 創辦人暨 CEO Andy Paul 仍持有一定份量股權，會繼續擔任 CEO 一職；目前來看 Corsair 未來將繼續保有一定的獨立性。<br />\n <br />\nCorsair 成立自 1994 年，長年專研電腦硬體暨電競周邊領域，囊括機殼、電源、風扇、耳麥組、鍵盤、散熱組件、耳機、滑鼠、電競椅等產品線，亦在電腦愛好者之間有相當知名度。<br />\n <br />\n本次交易預計在未來幾個月之內完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n消息來源：BusinessWire"},{"pid":"3d52598ac4df76fe1b3197096c48222d459b81a6","tid":339428,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T13:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1382db5e0b